CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774037478
OL,3,CMurder trial told evidence points to
OL,4,C'some other killer'
OL,6,FHe added: "It just doesn't add up, it
OL,7,Fis the stuff of reasonable doubt."
OL,9,FThe trial continues.
